&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href=&#34;http://www.baldanders.info/spiegel/log2/000812.shtml&#34;&gt;HTTPS Deep Inspection — Baldanders.info&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;

